hey linkuniversity and industry researchers in long- term basic research projects.&quot;andM;&quot;The Centers foster new knowledge and innovations in many important fields,scientific and technical fields that are crucial to our nation's future,&quot; headded.andM;(John McCormick/19911212/Press Contact: Cheryl Dybas, NSF, 202- 357-9498)</TEXT></DOC>